SQL_STMT_U.val: select Urut,objtype,cardcode,convert(date,docdate) docdate,DocNum,DocType,DocCurr,DocRate, ocrCode,CardName, AcctKas,AcctBank, iif(Urut=1,PayKas,0) KasAmt, iif(Urut=1,PayBank,0) BankAmt, BcgSum,TrackNo, AcctDtl,BaseAbs,InvType,DetailPayment,Discount,SELISIHkurs,WtSum, AcctCode,AcctName,AmtAdj,VatAmnt from ( select ROW_NUMBER () over (partition by x.DocNum order by x.DocDate,x.DocNum) Urut, * from (select h.objtype,h.cardcode,h.DocDate,h.DocNum,h.DocType,h.DocCurr,h.DocRate, d.ocrCode,isnull(g.CardName,h.CardName) CardName, iif(h.CashSum<>0,h.CashAcct,'') AcctKas, iif(h.TrsfrSum<>0,h.TrsfrAcct,h.CheckAcct) AcctBank, h.CashSum PayKas, h.CreditSum+h.CheckSum+h.TrsfrSum PayBank, h.BcgSum,h.TrackNo, IIF(H.DocType <> O.CardType,otrctlacct, DebPayAcct) AcctDtl,d.BaseAbs,d.InvType,d.SumApplied DetailPayment,d.DcntSum Discount,(H.DocRate - d.DocRate)*d.SumApplied AS SELISIHkurs,g.WtSum, c.AcctCode,c.AcctName,c.SumApplied AmtAdj,c.VatAmnt from ovpm h left join OCRD O ON O.CardCode=H.CardCode left join vpm2 d on d.docnum=h.docentry left join ogji g on g.DocEntry=d.DocEntry and d.InvType='1260' left join vpm4 c on c.docnum=h.docentry where convert(date,h.docdate) between ':1' and ':2' and h.Canceled='N' )x union all select ROW_NUMBER () over (partition by y.DocNum order by y.DocDate,y.DocNum) Urut,* from (select h.objtype,h.cardcode,h.DocDate,h.DocNum,h.DocType,h.DocCurr,h.DocRate, d.ocrCode,isnull(g.CardName,h.CardName) CardName, iif(h.CashSum<>0,h.CashAcct,'') AcctKas, iif(h.TrsfrSum<>0,h.TrsfrAcct,h.CheckAcct) AcctBank, h.CashSum PayKas, h.CreditSum+h.CheckSum+h.TrsfrSum PaymentBank, h.BcgSum,h.TrackNo, IIF(H.DocType <> O.CardType,otrctlacct, DebPayAcct) AcctDtl,d.BaseAbs,d.InvType,d.SumApplied DetailPayment,d.DcntSum Discount,(H.DocRate - d.DocRate)*d.SumApplied AS SELISIHkurs,g.WtSum, c.AcctCode,c.AcctName,c.SumApplied AmtAdj,c.VatAmnt from orct h left join OCRD O ON O.CardCode=H.CardCode left join rct2 d on d.docnum=h.docentry left join ogji g on g.DocEntry=d.DocEntry and d.InvType='1260' left join rct4 c on c.docnum=h.docentry where convert(date,h.docdate) between ':1' and ':2' and h.Canceled='N' )y )w where CardName like '%:3%' :4 order by AcctKas,AcctBank,docdate,DocNum,CardName
